Description: Modern note-taking application for Linux
 C0lorNote is a modern note-taking application inspired by macOS Notes
 and Google Keep. It offers a clean, efficient interface with rich text
 editing, tagging, categories, and both light and dark themes.
 .
 Features include:
  * Rich text editing (bold, italic, lists)
  * Organization with categories and tags
  * Full-text search
  * Light and dark themes
  * Note color coding
  * Export options (PDF, text)
  * Automatic saving

